nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.37

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.37 is the thirty-seventh issue of the 6th volume of the Star Wars Comic UK published on August 23, 2012. It came with free gifts, a Wookiee Bowcaster Force Attax cards and stickers. Features included a section on the Death Watch, Wookiee Puzzles, an episode guide to Friends and Enemies and Top Five Speeders.
The comic included the comic strip Incident on Kashyyyk.
